# ViralBoost AI - Website Functions and Systems (Web Info)

Is file me website ke pure functions, systems, aur capabilities simple Hinglish me diye gaye hain.

---

## 1) Website Kya Hai

ViralBoost AI ek creator + agency focused SaaS platform hai jo video content ko analyze, optimize, plan, aur monitor karne me help karta hai.

Primary goal:
- better content decisions
- higher viral potential
- faster workflow
- data-driven growth

---

## 2) Core User Functions (Website Kya Kar Sakti Hai)

### A) User Authentication and Account
- Email/password signup-login
