### Channel Intelligence Hub (March 30, 2026)
A comprehensive SaaS-style dashboard for YouTube channel analysis:

**Core Features:**
- 📊 Channel Overview - Basic stats (subscribers, views, engagement rate, growth %)
- 🏆 Channel Ranking System - Global rank, niche-based rank, growth momentum
- 💰 Revenue Calculator - Daily/monthly/yearly revenue estimates with CPM ranges by niche
- ⚔️ Competitor Comparison - Side-by-side comparison with up to 3 competitor channels
- 🧠 AI Insights - Actionable recommendations on strengths, improvements, and content strategy
- 📈 Growth Prediction - 30-day forecasts for subscribers, views, and revenue
- 📱 Modern UI/UX - Dark mode, glassmorphism, smooth animations, mobile responsive

**Ranking Formula:**
Score = (Subs × 0.3) + (Avg Views × 0.3) + (Engagement × 0.2) + (Upload Consistency × 0.2)

**User Benefits:**
- Understand channel position in minutes
- Compare against competition
- Identify growth opportunities
- Plan content strategy based on AI insights
- Estimate revenue potential
